casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al.

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $19,530 for the period June 1 through November 15, 1996, to be paid as follows: 30% by Nebraska, 30% by Wyoming, 15% by Colorado, and 25% by the United States. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 518 U. S. 1002.]
